						<p>Hero-stone (No. I) set up in the compound of the Basavēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>12th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This damaged stone about 12th century A.D. seems to record the death of a warrior in a fight details of which are lost.</p>						

